value.0: Leave me alone. I don't know you!
Greetings. I recognize a fellow Shadow Hopper.

Yes I could, as a matter of fact. 
Your skills have  me asking for a Target to be removed.

You are to recover a Brooch, stolen by a local robber hiding here in Freeport. He has hired a mercenary group and is attempting to move in on our control of Freeport.
Kill Kannovar and bring me the Brooch.
This Task will test your skills, so that I may ascertain if you will be of any use to us.

Yes I could, as a matter of fact.
Your skills have  me asking for an item to be retrieved.
You are to enter the Vault below this building and retrieve for me a gem. This Task will test your skills, so that I may ascertain if you will be of any use to us.
Ahh <FirstName>, Have you completed your Task and if so, then do you have something for me as proof?

Excellent! I'm sure he was no problem for you.
You have completed all the Tasks I have for you. Leave here and search out a higher ranked Guild House Master for further advancement in testing your skills.
Excellent! I'm sure his death will send ripples to our enemies. You can progress on to another Task.
We have made the decision to make the Official's Aid vanish. Remove him and return with proof. This must be accomplished with extreme discretion. Once he is gone we will have control of Freeport.

Excellent! I'm sure she was no problem for you.
You can progress on to another Task.

A Passenger traveling here by ship. His name is Eldicar and he must not be allowed to find out that his contact is dead. We have supplied a small fishing boat that will take you to a rendezvous with the ship before it makes dock. I will require his Signet Ring as proof of his demise. This must be a stealthy mission.
Take this token and find our man, he's waiting for you by the dock's.

Excellent! I'm sure he was no problem for you.
You can progress on to another Task.

What other task is there for an Assassin?
Your next Target is to be The Wife of a local Official here in Freeport. Keeva Le'Muire remove her quietly, be discreet.
Ahh <FirstName>, Have you completed your Task and if so, then do you have something for me as proof?

Excellent!
You have passed all of my Tasks.
You are indeed worthy to continue on from here and search out a higher ranked Guild House Master for further advancement in testing your skills.

Excellent!
